title: Add Decorative Details with the Classical Bead Router Bit
description:
Add Decorative Details with the Classical Bead Router Bit (59-502)
More Info:http://www.infinitytools.com/routing/router-bits/carbide/edge-making-router-bits/classical-bead-router-bits-3067
Blog: http://www.infinitytools.com/blog/2017/01/12/add-decorative-details-with-the-classical-bead-router-bit
Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/InfinityTools?sub_confirmation=1
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/InfinityCuttingTools/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/InfinityTools1
Instagram: @InfinityTools (https://www.instagram.com/infinitytools/)

Andrew Gibson shows you how this versatile classical bead router bit can dress up any furniture or cabinet project.

When paired with a 3/8"-radius cove bit, the moldings and decorative trim options become even more elegant.
